&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(58, 59, 65); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Engage the right decision-makers. You&#39;ll focus on owners, executives, and other decision-makers at contractor and merchant businesses across North America.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(58, 59, 65); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Shape how we go to market. You&#39;ll refine messaging, improve sales presentations, and help build our outbound motion as we scale. Your feedback directly influenc

