&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Build strong relationships with our internal Dealer Development partners and teams, as well as various stakeholders&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Resolve dealership concerns and existing loan issues that may arise by providing alternative solutions while using reason when dealing with emotional topics&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Assess loan documents and third party data to make informed lending decisions&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
